'''格蘭特·鮑勒'''（'''Grant Bowler'''，{{bd|1968年|7月18日}}）是一名在[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]出生的[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]演員<ref>{{cite news | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9900E3D9113DF937A35751C1A96F9C8B63 | title = What's On Today > 9 p.m. (ABC) ''Ugly Betty'' | first = Kathryn | last = Shattuck | date = December 4, 2009 | work = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | accessdate = October 25, 2012 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305032851/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9900E3D9113DF937A35751C1A96F9C8B63 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，他出生在紐西蘭，但活躍在美國、澳大利亞、紐西蘭和加拿大的電影、電視和舞台領域。

他較知名是在電視劇《''{{link-en|Blue Heelers|Blue Heelers}}''》中飾演{{link-en|Wayne Patterson|Wayne Patterson}}和《''{{link-en|Outrageous Fortune (TV series)|Outrageous Fortune (TV series)|Outrageous Fortune}}''》中的{{link-en|Wolfgang West|Wolfgang West}}。2010年11月，他宣佈成為《{{link-en|奪寶奇Show︰澳大利亞|The Amazing Race Australia}}》的主持人。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.ibtimes.com.au/grant-bowler-host-australia-amazing-race-1275960 |title = Grant Bowler to host Australia 'Amazing Race' |author = Lawrence Villamar |date = 2010-11-12 |publisher = International Business Times |language = en |accessdate = 2016-05-12 |archive-date = 2016-08-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160817041305/http://www.ibtimes.com.au/grant-bowler-host-australia-amazing-race-1275960 |dead-url = no }}</ref>他也在[[Syfy|Syfy]]的科幻電視劇《[[地球異世界|地球異世界]]》中飾演Joshua Nolan。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://deadline.com/2012/01/grant-bowler-cast-as-the-lead-in-new-syfy-series-defiance-215832/ |title = Grant Bowler Cast As The Lead In New Syfy Series 'Defiance' |author = Nellie Andreeva |date = 2012-01-17 |publisher = Deadline Hollywood |language = en |accessdate = 2016-05-12 |archive-date = 2016-06-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160603231354/http://deadline.com/2012/01/grant-bowler-cast-as-the-lead-in-new-syfy-series-defiance-215832/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

